财经十一人。
Eleven finance and economics.
由《财经》杂志公司产业报道团队创建，研讨企业成败，探究行业兴衰，推动阳光商业。
Founded by Caijing magazine's industry report team, it explores the success or failure of enterprises, probes into the ups and downs of the industry, and promotes sunshine business.
文·图 |《财经》记者 李斯洋编辑 | 马克2月6日，首批新型冠状病毒肺炎的重症患者于武汉金银潭医院正式接受新药瑞德西韦（Remdesivir）的临床测试。
Caijing & amp; Co. & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45;
2月5日下午，中国工程院院士、中日友好医院原院长王辰，中日友好医院呼吸与危重症医学科主任曹彬两名教授率队在武汉金银潭医院宣布：启动瑞德西韦三期临床研究，将有761例患者（其中轻、中症患者308例，重症患者435例）进入测试，并采用随机、双盲、安慰剂对照方法进行研究，以评价瑞德西韦在治疗新型冠状病毒感染的疗效和安全性。
On the afternoon of February 5, two professors, Wang Chen, academician of the Chinese Academy of Engineering and former director of the Sino-Japanese Friendship Hospital, and Cao Bin, director of respiratory and critical medicine at Wuhan Jiantan Hospital, announced that the Rhetsevir III clinical study will have 761 patients (308 of them mild and moderate cases and 435 severe cases) tested and evaluated its efficacy and safety in treating new coronavirus infections.
瑞德西韦是一款目前仍处于实验阶段的药物，由美国吉利德（Gilead）公司研发，原本用于治疗埃博拉病毒。
The drug, which is still in its experimental stage, was developed by Gilead in the United States and was originally designed to treat Ebola.
1月31日，《新英格兰医学杂志》（NEJM）称，在美国的一例重度新冠患者身上使用瑞德西韦后，症状得到显著缓解。
On January 31, the New England Journal of Medicine (NEJM) reported significant relief in the use of Rhetsevir in a case of severe crown disease in the United States.
基于“同情用药”原则，中国药监局很快批准了瑞德西韦的临床试验申请，并交由曹彬教授牵头组织临床测试。
Based on the principle of "compassionate medication," the Chinese Drug Administration quickly approved Radesiveh's application for clinical trials, which were led by Professor Cao Bin.
瑞德西韦何时能够广泛使用？曹彬2月6日向媒体表示，科学需要时间，不通过随机双盲临床研究没人敢确定疗效。
It will take time for science, and no one will be able to determine its effectiveness without a randomized double-blind clinical trial, Cao told reporters on Feb. 6.
吉利德公司也向媒体表示，因为对瑞德西韦对抗新型冠状病毒的疗效尚无足够了解，目前无法预测药物何时能被广泛使用。
Geely also told the press that it did not know enough about the efficacy of Rhetsevir in the fight against the new coronavirus and that it was not possible to predict when the drug would be widely used.
但吉利德表示，考虑到当前的紧迫情况，会采取多种措施增加供应。
However, given the urgency of the situation, Mr Gillid said various measures would be taken to increase supply.
2月4日下午，首批2843盒Remdesivir运抵北京。
The first 2,843 boxes of Remdesivir arrived in Beijing on the afternoon of 4 February.
进口通关单显示，瑞德西韦每支（150毫克）单价约20美元。
Import clearance slips show that Rhetsevir costs about $20 per unit (150 milligrams).
